Adds AssociationEnd C<reception> values.
Elements of C<@val> must of type L<UMMF::UML::MetaModel::Behavioral_Elements::Common_Behavior::Reception|UMMF::UML::MetaModel::Behavioral_Elements::Common_Behavior::Reception>.
